{"tid":1902192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"* 現在我宣佈召集全球港人組織國際鍵盤戰線對抗星馬共匪*","createTime":"2020-02-28T08:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T17:10:03.000Z","uid":235519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2af97a4a4bb3222c35e222dbda75841d901433","tid":1902192,"uid":235519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"自從光復運動開始之後，相信有留意藍華早報Facebook page嘅手足都會見過好多星加坡同埋馬來西亞嘅華人冷血涼薄嘅留言以及種種嘅嬉笑怒罵去攻擊我地香港人。<br />\n<br />\n基本上我常常屌撚柒鳩佢地，但好可惜對方往往都係人多勢眾，常常不幸被圍剿。現在我想召集各位一齊上去南華早報Facebook page問候下呢班垃圾冚家剷。<br />\n支持差佬加人工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食屎啦仆街<br />\n有圖有真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSqRfGm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSqRfGm.png&h=dd79ddca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRAeds3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRAeds3.png&h=bf1c2db5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SguFTs4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSguFTs4.png&h=fa8b2f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvu6O1r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkvu6O1r.png&h=356fc2b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df2b8e664c7835c1046f486f8cae48bf2770b3c9","tid":1902192,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"【手足入嚟幫手廣傳】突發 「一加二等於三」行動！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902159</a>"},{"pid":"e5c1929e41a7ac7175cfff7970ae70029d10f197","tid":1902192,"uid":235519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:18:53.000Z","msg":"推推推，唔好俾佢沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c